<section id="writingtask1">

<p class="popuptext"><b>Writing Task 2</b></p>
<p class="popuptext"> You should spend about 40 minutes on this task.</p>
<p class="popuptext"> Present a written argument or case to an educated reader with no specialist knowledge of the following topic.</p>
<p class="popuptext"><b>Increasing numbers of workers are suffering from stress and stress-related illness. Why is the modern workplace so stressful, and what can be done to reduce this problem?</b></p>
<p class="popuptext"><b> To what extent do you agree or disagree?</b></p>

<p class="popuptext">You should write at least 250 words</p>
<p class="popuptext">You should use your own ideas, knowledge and experience and support your arguments with examples and relevant evidence.</p>

		</section>
		
<section id="fb0">
  <p align="left">
    <b>Causes of the problem</b>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">1:  Increased workloads and tighter deadlines</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">3:  Rapid pace of technological change in the workplace</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">9:  Lack of job security</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left"/>
  <p align="left">
    <b>Possible solutions to the problem</b>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">2:  Avoidance of unnecessary change</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">4:  More legal protection to ensure job security</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">5:  Realistic workloads and deadlines agreed on by management and employees</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">6:  Legislation to limit working hours</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">7:  Provision of training and support for new technology</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font color="#000000">8:  Greater commitment from employers</font>
  </p>
